description:
We’ve got another special episode for you this week packed with never before heard recordings from two hilarious guests, Tiffany Haddish and Regina Hall, the stars of the movie Girls Trip out July 21st! In “The Lost Tapes Vol. 2”, Tiffany Haddish (Girls Trip, The Carmichael Show) discusses how she conquered bullies growing up and shows Anna and Sim the new “gadget” she bought on Amazon! Then, they call Hilary, whose fiancé’s family makes her feel like an outsider and Tiffany teaches the group a new word. Later, Regina Hall (Girls Trip, Scary Movie), Anna, and Sim talk to Chrissy, who is struggling with the fact that she isn’t into relationships. Tune in and enjoy!
